&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a motivated individual to join the Fracture Clinic in Wythenshawe Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be keen on delivering patient centred care in a fast paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Educated at NVQ Level 3, the post holder will be an essential team member in caring for our patients in the Fracture Clinic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder must have an interest in completing the Plaster Technician training in due course. The successful candidate will join a well formed team composed of a variety of staff members and will have the fantastic opportunity to develop their skills alongside world renowned clinicians.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enquiries welcome on 0161 291 4295, Alexandra Pinzar, Nurse Manager or on 0161 291 6162, Sarah Body, Sister in Charge in Fracture Clinic.&lt;/p&gt;
